Troubleshooting
Common Issues
Symptom	Cause	Solution	
`AGENT_RUNTIME_VERSION not set`	Missing .env	`cp .env.template .env`	
Model timeouts	Low timeout values	Increase `FUNCTION_TIMEOUT_*`	
SQLite locked	Concurrent access	Use `STATE_STORAGE_TYPE=postgresql`	
Permission denied	Wrong Azure credentials	Run `az login --service-principal`	
Subagent failures	Network isolation	Check `AGENT_MAX_CONCURRENT_TASKS`	

